ito Santo</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note5a\" data-full-marker=\"5a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201382\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.24?lang=por#p24\">2 Né. 25:24</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.13-14?lang=por#p13\">Al. 34:13–14</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note5b\" data-full-marker=\"5b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201383\" id=\"note5b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/35.2?lang=por#p2\">Êx. 35:2</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/sabbath-day?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Dia do Sábado (Dia de Descanso)</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note5c\" data-full-marker=\"5c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201384\" id=\"note5c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/profanity?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Profanidade</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"d\" id=\"note5d\" data-full-marker=\"5d\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201385\" id=\"note5d_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/blaspheme-blasphemy?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Blasfemar, Blasfêmia</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201386\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/7.24?lang=por#p24\">Jacó 7:24</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/enos/1.20?lang=por#p20\">En. 1:20</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"7\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note7a\" data-full-marker=\"7a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124201387\" id=\"note7a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/1.9,11,15?lang=por#p9\">Jacó 1:9, 11, 15</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note7b\" data-full-mark